export const getLang = (lang) => LANGS[lang]
export const getLangs = () => Object.values(LANGS)
export const api = ({ query, source, target }) => `${GOOGLE_TRANSLATE_API}&sl=${source}&tl=${target}&dt=t&q=${encodeURI(query)}`
